<Layout 
  title="Aircraft Squad Building" 
  description="Aircraft squad building guide for Last War: Survival."
>
  <h1>Aircraft Squad Building</h1>

  <QuickSummary>
    <p>Aircraft squads are excellent counters to many Tank-heavy compositions. Detailed hero focus orders and builds coming soon.</p>
  </QuickSummary>

  <h2>Core Principles for Aircraft</h2>
  <ul class="text-sm space-y-1">
    <li>Aircraft excels at burst and can counter many Tank squads when built correctly.</li>
    <li>Focus order typically prioritizes strong backline DPS and support like DVA, Carlie, Schuyler, etc. (exact order varies by season).</li>
    <li>Positioning is critical — Aircraft often wants different front/back priorities than Tank.</li>
  </ul>

  <p class="mt-4 text-sm">Detailed hero focus order, skill priorities, and a community-made visual guide coming soon.</p>

  <div class="mt-6">
    <a href="/squad-building" class="text-[#f59e0b]">← Back to Squad Building Principles</a>
  </div>
</Layout>